<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Pokécard Palace | Home</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css">

<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>


        <div class="container mt-2">
            <div class="jumbotron">
                <h1 class="display-4">Pokécard Palace</h1>

                <p class="lead box-links">
                    Here you can find a wide selection of Pokémon trading cards
                    from various generations and series. Whether you're a seasoned collector or just starting
                    out, we have something for everyone. If you encounter any issues, have questions, or
                    need assistance, please <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>.

                    <hr class="my-4 custom-hr">

                <p>Explore our site using the buttons below!</p>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-4 mt-2">
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block rounded shadow-lg">Random Card </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-4 mt-2">
                            <a href="/collections" class="btn btn-primary btn-block rounded shadow-lg">Browse
                                Collection</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-4 mt-2">
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block rounded shadow-lg">Contact Us</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Using Target blank here to ensure they open on new tab, can adjust depending on spec etc -->
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-1">
                    <div class="styled-box box-links shadow-lg">
                        <h3>Newcomers</h3>
                        <p>Are you new to Pokémon card collecting? Check out these resources to get started:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-tcg/play-online/" target="_blank">Pokémon
                                    TCG Online</a></li>
                            <li><a href="https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-tcg/rules/" target="_blank">Official
                                    Pokémon
                                    TCG Rules</a></li>
                            <li><a href="https://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Introduction_to_the_Pok%C3%A9mon_Trading_Card_Game"
                                    target="_blank">Bulbapedia: Introduction to the Pokémon TCG</a>
                            </li>
                            <li><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/pkmntcg/" target="_blank">Reddit: Pokémon TCG
                                    Subreddit</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>


                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-1">
                    <div class="styled-box box-links shadow-lg">
                        <h3>Why Collect Pokémon Cards?</h3>
                        <p>There are various reasons why individuals might choose to collect Pokémon cards, and here are
                            a few of them:</p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>For those who cherish the nostalgia of collecting</li>
                            <li>To battle with friends through the physical game</li>
                            <li>For collectors who seek to turn their passion into profit</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mt-2">
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 custom-card shadow-lg">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/card1.png" alt="Paldean Fates Card Promo">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Paldean Fates</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Shine Bright in
                                Scarlet & Violet—Paldean Fates</p>
                            <a href="https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-news/shine-bright-with-mimikyu-gardevoir-ex-charizard-ex-and-more-in-scarlet-violet-paldean-fates"
                                class="btn btn-primary">Go to External Article</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 custom-card shadow-lg">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/card2.jpeg" alt="Darkrai">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Pokémon GO</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Darkrai Pokémon GO Raid Battle Tips</p>
                            <a href="https://www.pokemon.com/us/strategy/darkrai-pokemon-go-raid-battle-tips"
                                class="btn btn-primary">Go to External Article</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 custom-card shadow-lg">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/card3.png" alt="Prize Pack Promo">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Prize Packs</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Pokémon Prize Packs Series Four</p>
                            <a href="https://www.pokemon.com/us/pokemon-news/receive-play-pokemon-prize-packs-series-four-at-your-local-game-store"
                                class="btn btn-primary">Go to External Article</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>


            <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
                integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
                crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
            <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js"
                integrity="sha384-ZMP7rVo3mIykV+2+9J3UJ46jBk0WLaUAdn689aCwoqbBJiSnjAK/l8WvCWPIPm49"
                crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
            <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js"
                integrity="sha384-ChfqqxuZUCnJSK3+MXmPNIyE6ZbWh2IMqE241rYiqJxyMiZ6OW/JmZQ5stwEULTy"
                crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>

</html>